sentences: Lokua Kanza (born April 1958) is a singer-songwriter from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.
Lokua Kanza was born Pascal Lokua Kanza in Bukavu in the province of Sud-Kivu, in the eastern part of the Democratic Republic of Congo.
In 1964, the family went to live in Kinshasa in a middle class area, until the day when Pascal's father, a ship's captain, died.
